        padding: 8px; 
        text-align: center; ">Ordered At</th>
                                <th style="border: 1px solid #cccccc; 
        padding: 8px; 
        text-align: center; ">Delivery Date</th>
                                <th style="border: 1px solid #cccccc; 
        padding: 8px; 
        text-align: center; ">Payment Status</th>
